text: Bumpers is a surname. It may refer to: *Betty Bumpers (1925–2018), American activist, First Lady of Arkansas, from 1971 to 1975 as wife of Dale Bumpers *Dale Bumpers (1925–2016), American politician, Governor of Arkansas (1971–1975), Senator (1975–1999) ==See also== *Dale Bumpers College of Agricultural, Food and Life Sciences *Bumper (disambiguation)
title: Bumpers (name)
